                <head>5. Editorial Note</head>
                <p>On February 7 the President approved Supplement I to <gloss target="#t_NSC1"
                        >NSC</gloss> 5803 entitled “Statement of Policy on U.S. Policy on Berlin.”
                    The text is virtually identical to that in Supplement I to <gloss
                        target="#t_NSC1">NSC</gloss> 5727, December 13, 1957, printed in <ref
                        target="frus1955-57v26#pg_521">
                        <hi rend="italic">Foreign Relations</hi>, 1955–1957, volume XXVI, pages
                        521</ref>–<ref target="frus1955-57v26#pg_525">525</ref>.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
